  "source_notes": "Sy Scholfield quotes him with Jonathan Bazzi in a thread on Twitter X: \"\\nBazzi: \"Il 13 giugno dell’85, ore 10.10 del mattino – Sole in Gemelli, ascendente Leone, Luna in Ariete – la Tina mi accompagnava da quest’altra parte, un paio di settimane fuori dal termine previsto (sarei nato lo stesso sotto Mercurio). Finora è stato un discreto casino\"\\n\\n(Translation: On 13 June 1985, at 10:10 in the morning - Sun in Gemini, Leo ascendant, Moon in Aries - Tina accompanied me to this other side, a couple of weeks outside the expected time (I would have been born under Mercury anyway). So far it's been quite a mess) (posted on his birthday, 13 June 2023) [https://x.com/jonathanbazzi/status/1668639023139545090].\\n\\nCoppola commented: \"Hey Jonny, my friend. Io sono nato alle 5 e solo da quell'ora riesco a lavorare davvero. Dici che è la tua teoria del travaglio e lo scopro solo ora?\\n(Translation: Hey Jonny, my friend. I was born at 5 and only from that time on I can actually work. You say it's your labor theory and I'm just finding out now?) [https://x.com/massimcoppola/status/1360278628790128649].\\n",
